microsoftLearnIssueBody:
Microsoft Learn is a brand-new platform and we are striving to improve the content and experiences based on customer responses.

We want to hear from you!

Please fill out the following information for us:
1. The issue or feedback you are reporting about.
2. Anything else you would like to tell us.

Note: While we are not directly responding to all customers at this time, please note that we are reviewing any and all feedback that is coming in.
